        "description": "<p>Authorizes the DDoS Response Team (DRT) to access the specified Amazon S3 bucket containing your AWS WAF logs. You can associate up to 10 Amazon S3 buckets with your subscription.</p> <p>To use the services of the DRT and make an <code>AssociateDRTLogBucket</code> request, you must be subscribed to the <a href=\"https://aws.amazon.com/premiumsupport/business-support/\">Business Support plan</a> or the <a href=\"https://aws.amazon.com/premiumsupport/enterprise-support/\">Enterprise Support plan</a>.</p>",
